config BR2_PACKAGE_PARKINSOUND_STEPGATE
	bool "parkinsound-stepgate"
	help
	  Parkinsound Step Gate - a 16-step audio gate sequencer LV2
	  plugin for MOD devices.

	  Each step exposes an On/Off toggle and a Tie toggle (legato vs.
	  half-step cut). The step clock follows the host BPM via the LV2
	  time:Position extension, with a tempo control fallback for free
	  running operation.

	  https://github.com/pilali/Parkinsound
